"04120211.xhp\n"
"par_id41550528154857\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Use <menuitem>вҖңAdditional StylesвҖқ</menuitem> to include paragraphs in the Table of Contents with the вҖңFigure Index HeadingвҖқ or вҖңBibliography HeadingвҖқ paragraph style, as well as any other relevant paragraph style."
